{{!--
     SHARED big-editorial-card body. (Handlebars comment, not an HTML comment:
     this partial is rendered twice, and an HTML comment would be emitted twice
     into the README.) Called with a project array as context:
       {{> project-cards _flagshipProjects}}   (featured-work.hbs — "What I build")
       {{> project-cards _clientCardProjects}} (commissioned.hbs — client work)
     Both sections must render IDENTICALLY — priority is expressed by order on
     the page, not by card size — so this markup exists exactly once. Per card:
     logo (right-float 80px) · H3 name · "For <org>" line · impact headline ·
     optional related-project cross-links.
     2026-07-15: the 18px tech-stack icon strip (_featuredStackResolved) was
     REMOVED from every README surface — Chan found the logo rows cluttered. The
     data (meta.x_brand.featuredStack + meta.x_brand.techIconMap) is still in the
     shards and still resolved by build.mjs into dist/profile.json; only the
     rendering is gone. Do not confuse it with _contextLogo (which harnesses a
     product supports) or _affiliationOrg (the commissioning client) — those stay.
     GOTCHA: keep the blank line between the bare <img> and the following `###`
     heading — CommonMark's type-7 HTML-block rule swallows the heading without it.
--}}
{{#each this}}{{#if logo}}<img src="{{logo}}" align="right" height="80" alt="{{name}}" title="{{name}}">

{{/if}}### [{{briefTagline name}}]({{default url repoUrl}})

{{#if _affiliationOrg}}<sub>For <a href="{{_affiliationOrg.url}}"><picture><source media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)" srcset="{{default _affiliationOrg.logoDark _affiliationOrg.logoLight}}"><img src="{{_affiliationOrg.logoLight}}" height="22" alt="{{_affiliationOrg.name}}"></picture> {{_affiliationOrg.name}}</a>{{#if _affiliationOrg.context}} — {{_affiliationOrg.context}}{{/if}}.</sub>
{{else}}{{#if _contextLogo.length}}<sub>For {{#each _contextLogo}}<a href="{{url}}"><img src="{{src}}" height="22" alt="{{alt}}" style="vertical-align:middle"> {{alt}}</a>{{#unless @last}} · {{/unless}}{{/each}}.</sub>
{{else}}{{#if entity}}<sub>{{entity}}.</sub>
{{/if}}{{/if}}{{/if}}

{{#if narrative.impactHeadline}}{{narrative.impactHeadline}}

{{else}}{{briefTagline tagline}}

{{/if}}{{#if _relatedProjects.length}}<sub>↳ Related: {{#each _relatedProjects}}<a href="{{default url repoUrl}}">{{briefTagline name}} ↗</a>{{#unless @last}} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {{/unless}}{{/each}}</sub>

{{/if}}<br clear="all">

{{/each}}
